117
00:06:54,030 --> 00:06:58,110
So first thing we want to do here is keep track of cash.

118
00:06:58,110 --> 00:07:00,900
So we get $6,000.

119
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:01,955
Now, is this revenue?

120
00:07:01,955 --> 00:07:04,670


